{
  "texts": [
    "Each set consisted of the original, ChatGPT 3.5-generated and ChatGPT 4-generated abstracts and was evaluated by two of the authors.",
    "To standardise abstract scoring, the first 5 sets of abstracts were evaluated as a group whereby any misconception of the checklist was clarified.",
    "Following this, if there was any disagreement in the abstract assessment, this was discussed and resolved with an independent evaluator, SK.",
    "Continuous data was presented as mean average, proportion (%), simple coefficients and 95% confidence interval, when applicable.",
    "Paired T-test was conducted to compare the mean OQS of the original, GPT 3.5-and GPT 4-generated abstracts, meanwhile Pearson's χ2 test assessed the proportion of abstracts adherent to the CONSORT-A items and readability."
  ]
}